        <article id="post-14704" class="post-14704 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-news-items tag-barack-obama tag-chamber-of-commerce tag-crony-capitalism tag-export-import-bank tag-financial-services-roundtable tag-kevin-mccarthy tag-steve-scalise clearfix rtp-post-box">
            
            <header class="post-header ">
                
                                            <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/06/24/officials-at-the-ex-im-bank-are-being-investigated-as-it-faces-a-serious-fight-for-survival/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Officials at the Ex-Im Bank are Under Investigation as it Fights for Survival">Officials at the Ex-Im Bank are Under Investigation as it Fights for Survival</a></h2>
                <?php// rtp_hook_end_post_title(); ?>

                
            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-top"><span class="author"><a class="fn" href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/author/mkriegs/" title="Posts by Michael Krieger">Michael Krieger</a></span> <span class="rtp-meta-separator">|</span> Posted <time class="published" datetime="2014-06-24T12:46:07+00:00">Tuesday Jun 24, 2014</time> at 12:46 pm         <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/06/24/officials-at-the-ex-im-bank-are-being-investigated-as-it-faces-a-serious-fight-for-survival/#comments" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on Officials at the Ex-Im Bank are Under Investigation as it Fights for Survival"><span>2</span> Comments</a></span>
            </div><!-- .post-meta -->            </header><!-- .post-title -->

            <div class="post-content">
                                

                
                <p><img class="alignleft  wp-image-14726" src="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Screen-Shot-2014-06-24-at-12.37.37-PM-180x118.jpg" alt="Screen Shot 2014-06-24 at 12.37.37 PM" width="156" height="102" />The Export-Import bank isn&#8217;t a big issue for me. In fact, I&#8217;ve barely given it much thought at all over the years. The reason I&#8217;ve decided to write on it today is because the federally backed bank, which has been around since 1934, faces a very serious threat to its survival.</p>
<p>I think the most important aspect of this entire fight is the fact that on opposite sides of the debate are not Democrats versus Republicans, but once again Republicans vs. Republicans (as in the<strong> <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/06/13/is-charlie-rangel-the-next-to-go-22-term-new-york-democrat-faces-serious-primary-threat/">Dave Brat vs. Eric Cantor race</a></strong>). We again see tea party Republicans facing off against establishment RINOs. On one side we hear claims by the tea party wing that the Ex-Im merely serves as a conduit for crony capitalism and favoritism to large corporations, or those willing to bribe officials. On the other side, we see establishment Republicans, who are extremely cozy with mega-corporations, maintaing that the institution plays a crucial role in financing American exports to make them competitive.</p>
<p> <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/06/24/officials-at-the-ex-im-bank-are-being-investigated-as-it-faces-a-serious-fight-for-survival/#more-14704" class="more-link">Read the Full Article »</a></p>
<div style=display:inline-block;>
<div style=float:left;margin-right:6px;>
<a href=bitcoin:1LefuVV2eCnW9VKjJGJzgZWa9vHg7Rc3r1><img src=http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/lbk-post-donations.png></a>
</div>
